nodes.text: Sector 885. 2J99 was a subsector located in the Lothal sector of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. During the rule of the Galactic Empire, the Lothal sector and its subsectors, including Sector 885. 2J99, were ruled by the Empire and controlled by Moff Stattata and Governor Arihnda Pryce, a human female from the planet Lothal.
